   Kotwice = atrybut id (weasyprint tworzy named destinations): info.pdf#FID1_831, #R05.
   Uruchamiać: DYLD_FALLBACK_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/homebrew/lib python3 _build_info_pdf.py
"""
